platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Mika Mobile has crafted a superb and wonderfully robust role-playing game in Battleheart Legacy. Each hero can equip a diverse assortment of abilities, ranging from devastating spells to adept swordsmanship and stealthy rogue attacks. The game’s flexible combat system allows you to freely mix skills and spells as you slay hordes of goblins, bats, and skeletons. Battleheart Legacy is a polished, beautifully animated game with a wealth of places to explore and plenty of ways to play.
